operly and support the following browser configurations for administrator u=
sers:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style=3D"margin-left: 12.0px;"><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><s=
pan>Mozilla=C2=AE Firefox=C2=AE, most recent stable version* (t</span>ested=
 on Firefox </span><span>33<span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><span style=
=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">)</span></span></span></p></li>
<li style=3D"margin-left: 12.0px;"><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><s=
pan>Google Chrome=E2=84=A2, most recent stable version* (t</span>ested on C=
hrome </span><span>38<span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">)</span></span></p>=
</li>
<li style=3D"margin-left: 12.0px;"><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Mi=
crosoft=C2=AE Internet Explorer=C2=AE versions<span style=3D"color: rgb(51,=
51,51);">&nbsp;9, 10 and 11&nbsp;<span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">(tested=
 mainly on IE 11</span><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">)*</span></span><=
/span></p></li>
<li style=3D"margin-left: 12.0px;"><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><s=
